'''Muzik Aktif''' ({{lang-ms|Active Music}}) is a music [[television channel|channel]] in [[Television in Malaysia|Malaysia]]. It is the first Malaysian music channel, and one of the first Malaysian digital channels. It launched on the Astro platform in 16 March 2009<ref name="Bernama">http://www.bernama.com/bernama/v5/newsindex.php?id=394530</ref>.

